{"tid":2463021,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國確定對澳洲葡萄酒開徵反傾銷稅 100-212% 為期5年","createTime":"2021-03-26T11:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T12:29:57.000Z","uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"14828e5793619b161683f07a8c011a80b5d351cd","tid":2463021,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"根據公告附件，澳洲葡萄酒公司分別被課以稅率不等的反傾銷稅，其中最低的是天鵝釀酒有限公司（Australia Swan Vintage Pty Ltd）的116.2%；大多數公司則被課徵167.1%；最高稅率達218.4%。<br />\n<br />\n中澳兩國交惡後，2020年7月6日，中國酒業協會代表國內葡萄酒產業，對澳洲進口葡萄酒提出反補貼調查的申請。2020年8月18日，中國商務部決定進行反傾銷立案調查<br />\n<br />\n2020年11月27日，中國商務部發布初裁公告，初步認定澳洲進口葡萄酒存在傾銷，開始徵收107.1%至212.1%的臨時反傾銷保證金；去年12月11日起再開徵6.3%至6.4%臨時反補貼稅保證金。<br />\n<br />\n中國商務部今天發布的最終裁定，等於宣告澳洲葡萄酒將被擋在門外長達5年。"},{"pid":"d6a637e284af26781019b617e8dad350d57d98d2","tid":2463021,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:23:03.000Z","msg":"港共跟唔跟"},{"pid":"a075730f3babad2fd282f676ddb69e08f469f65e","tid":2463021,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6a637e284af26781019b617e8dad350d57d98d2","tid":2463021,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:23:03.000Z","msg":"港共跟唔跟"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:27:26.000Z","msg":"陳茂球飲乜？"},{"pid":"84c50302ee509423bac1f8e98d8240016237f237","tid":2463021,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a075730f3babad2fd282f676ddb69e08f469f65e","tid":2463021,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6a637e284af26781019b617e8dad350d57d98d2","tid":2463021,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:23:03.000Z","msg":"港共跟唔跟"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:27:26.000Z","msg":"陳茂球飲乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/http://www.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/laughing.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%